Paste your SonarCloud user token on a single line in a file named ".sonar-token"
(no quotes, no extra whitespace). That file is gitignored and must never be committed.

Generate a token at: https://sonarcloud.io/account/security

  cp .sonar-token.example .sonar-token
  # then replace the contents of .sonar-token with your token

Alternatively, export it for the current shell instead of using a file:

  export SONAR_TOKEN=<your-token>
